response.overview: The following is a collection of media related to the Paranormal Inquisitors, a once-popular online content creation team.  This documentation includes videos originally shared with public, as well as previously unseen footage taken from the group's recovered digital memory cards.  All footage - both the publicly shared videos and the newly recovered files from memory cards - have been edited only for time and otherwise remain unchanged and presented in their original forms.
response.title: Of The Woodlands
